WEBVTT

00:15.160 --> 00:17.600
[goats bleating]

00:43.240 --> 00:45.280
[Balotelli]
Dear nephew,

00:45.360 --> 00:47.680
hope you haven't resorted to piracy yet.

00:47.760 --> 00:49.680
Although, after three years in Norway,

00:49.760 --> 00:52.080
I wish I had.

00:52.160 --> 00:54.000
Like the albinos of Lagos,

00:54.080 --> 00:57.400
we are isolated
from the rest of the society,

00:57.480 --> 01:00.760
and they break our spirits
by humiliating us,

01:00.840 --> 01:03.160
a process they call "integration."

01:04.840 --> 01:07.560
They say Norway is a cold country.

01:07.640 --> 01:12.520
So far, the worst cold I have felt
has not come from the climate

01:12.600 --> 01:15.480
but from the hearts of the Norwegians.

01:17.240 --> 01:18.760
But you know your uncle.

01:18.840 --> 01:22.400
- I never lose my faith in humanity.
- [engine racing]

01:22.480 --> 01:25.360
[in Norwegian]
Look out, nigger!

01:25.440 --> 01:28.120
[in English]
Foolish man. What did I do?

01:28.200 --> 01:30.920
No nothing.

01:36.600 --> 01:38.480
[in Norwegian]
What did you say?

01:39.160 --> 01:42.920
[theme song playing]

02:14.840 --> 02:17.640
[Billy Joel's
"Only the Good Die Young" playing]

02:22.400 --> 02:24.160
[Torgeir in Norwegian]
So I'm sitting in the audience,

02:24.240 --> 02:27.840
and then the business guru brings me up
in front of everyone

02:27.920 --> 02:30.680
and says, "Torgeir,
how do we solve this problem?"

02:30.760 --> 02:33.440
He wants me to peel a banana.

02:33.520 --> 02:35.640
Easy peasy, I figure, and go at it,

02:35.720 --> 02:37.880
and he's all like, "No, no, no!"

02:37.960 --> 02:39.080
Wrong.

02:39.160 --> 02:42.360
Then he plays a video showing
how a gorilla does it.

02:42.440 --> 02:43.840
And wouldn't you know,

02:43.920 --> 02:46.040
the monkey does it
the complete opposite way.

02:46.120 --> 02:48.240
Like this!

02:48.320 --> 02:49.840
[in English]
So, you know...

02:49.920 --> 02:51.480
Much easier. Much easier.

02:51.560 --> 02:53.480
So let me get this straight.

02:53.560 --> 02:57.320
I pay you to take a business seminar,

02:57.400 --> 02:59.520
and you learn how to peel a banana?

02:59.600 --> 03:02.760
Jesus, the banana
is a metaphor, you know.

03:02.840 --> 03:04.440
It-- The gorilla teaches us

03:04.520 --> 03:07.240
to see the problem with--
from a different angle.

03:07.320 --> 03:08.720
Okay, that's it.

03:08.800 --> 03:10.320
No more school for you.

03:10.400 --> 03:12.360
These big words
are causing brain damage.

03:12.440 --> 03:14.520
- [camera clicks]
- Oh, fuck.

03:14.600 --> 03:17.040
How fast was I going?

03:17.120 --> 03:18.440
Okay, fast.

03:19.680 --> 03:21.080
Great.

03:21.160 --> 03:24.920
Who am I gonna have to buy
to get out of this one?

03:25.000 --> 03:27.320
Damn it.

03:27.400 --> 03:31.520
But, boss, maybe if you start
thinking like a monkey,

03:31.600 --> 03:36.080
you will see the problem
with different perspective.

03:36.160 --> 03:38.960
[Jan in Norwegian]
The point of the discrimination-ball

03:39.040 --> 03:43.120
is that we can make fun of everything.

03:43.200 --> 03:48.160
By kidding around within
a safe confine like this,

03:48.240 --> 03:51.800
we take the sting out of the bad words.

03:51.880 --> 03:53.920
Take that, chocolate man.

03:55.840 --> 03:57.920
- [Laban] White ass.
- [laughs]

03:58.000 --> 04:01.360
Good one! Brownie.

04:01.440 --> 04:04.920
- Potato.
- You see?

04:05.000 --> 04:07.200
The bad words lose all meaning!

04:07.280 --> 04:09.760
Jungle bunny.

04:09.840 --> 04:11.080
Fucking cunt.

04:13.680 --> 04:15.600
That's not cool, Balotelli.

04:15.680 --> 04:17.400
Why not?

04:17.480 --> 04:19.400
That phrase is gender discrimination.

04:19.480 --> 04:22.320
Today's topic is racism,
so we joke only about racism.

04:22.400 --> 04:26.800
Those are the rules you need to learn
if you want to be Norwegian.

04:26.880 --> 04:28.320
- Norwegian!
- [Jan] Where are you going?

04:28.400 --> 04:30.800
Balotelli.

04:30.880 --> 04:32.760
He's responsible for the food today.

04:32.840 --> 04:34.720
