- [laughs]

04:36.200 --> 04:37.960
Mussel.

04:39.680 --> 04:40.760
Asshole.

04:46.720 --> 04:49.240
[in English] You wanna speed things up,
bananas for brains?

04:49.320 --> 04:51.840
